episodes.title: Orioles owner responds to Epstein files mention
episodes.description:
David Rubenstein, the owner of the Baltimore Orioles and founder of The Carlyle Group, is named in the Jeffrey Epstein files. However, Rubenstein is not accused of any wrongdoing. Emails show Rubenstein met with Epstein for dinner in November 2012. It appears they intended to meet again for dinner later that month; however, it appears the second meeting did not actually take place.
